1
00:00:15,759 --> 00:00:20,100
택시 창밖으로 번지는 불빛
Lights blurring outside the taxi window

2
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:25,440
라디오에서 흘러나온 옛날 노래
An old song played on the radio

3
00:00:26,260 --> 00:00:31,760
이 시간엔 모든 게 느려져
At this hour, everything slows down

4
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:35,840
너한테 갈까 말까 고민만 해
I just agonize over whether to go to you or not

5
00:00:37,439 --> 00:00:41,140
편의점 앞 벤치에 앉아서
Sitting on a bench in front of the convenience store

6
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:46,560
따뜻한 캔 하나 손에 쥐고
Holding a warm can in my hand

7
00:00:48,439 --> 00:00:52,899
네 연락을 기다리는 건 아닌데
I'm not waiting for your call, but

8
00:00:52,899 --> 00:00:55,420
자꾸 화면을 확인하게 돼
I keep checking my screen

9
00:00:55,439 --> 00:00:57,100
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
Two AM, a night where the frequencies align

10
00:00:58,439 --> 00:01:03,399
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I hear your voice through the static

11
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:08,359
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we are awake

12
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:13,319
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
In different places under the same sky

13
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:18,280
옥상에서 내려다본 골목길
The alley viewed from the rooftop

14
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:22,594
가로등 하나가 깜빡이고 있어
A streetlamp is flickering

15
00:01:22,594 --> 00:01:25,590
하고 싶은 말은 루프처럼 돌아
The words I want to say loop endlessly

16
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:31,579
입 밖으론 한마디도 못 꺼내
I can't utter a single word

17
00:01:31,659 --> 00:01:36,400
이어폰 한쪽만 끼고 걸어
I walk with only one earbud in

18
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:41,140
네가 좋아하던 그 노래 틀어
Playing that song you liked

19
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:45,319
발걸음이 리듬을 타는 밤
A night where my footsteps follow the rhythm

20
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:50,260
혼자인데 혼자가 아닌 것 같아
I'm alone, but it doesn't feel like I am

21
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:55,799
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
Two AM, a night where the frequencies align

22
00:01:56,859 --> 00:02:00,980
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I hear your voice through the static

23
00:02:03,859 --> 00:02:06,340
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we are awake

24
00:02:07,919 --> 00:02:11,860
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
In different places under the same sky

25
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:17,280
전화할까 말까 세 번째 고민
Should I call or not, my third dilemma

26
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:22,120
나도 지금 네 번호 보고 있어
I'm also looking at your number right now

27
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:27,680
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
Two AM, a night where the frequencies align

28
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:32,919
잡음 속에서 결국 너를 찾아
In the static, I finally find you

29
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,979
이 도시가 잠들어도 우리는 깨어서
Even if this city sleeps, we are awake

30
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:38,800
같은 주파수로 이어져 있어
Connected by the same frequency

